@WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5296

### Weather Forecast (Exemplo)
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### ========================================
### EXPENSES - Gerenciamento de Despesas
### ========================================

### 1. Criar nova despesa
POST {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": 1,
  "year": 2025,
  "description": "Compra no supermercado",
  "amount": 250.50,
  "category": "Alimenta誽o",
  "status": "Pago",
  "paymentMethod": "Cart緌 de Cr嶮ito"
}

###

### 2. Buscar todas as despesas (GET - SEM BODY)
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Buscar despesas com filtros (GET - SEM BODY)
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense?month=1&year=2025&category=Alimenta誽o
Accept: application/json

###

### 3.1. Buscar apenas por m瘰 e ano
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense?month=1&year=2025
Accept: application/json

###

### 3.2. Buscar apenas por categoria
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense?category=Transporte
Accept: application/json

###

### 3.3. Buscar por status
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense?status=Pago
Accept: application/json

###

### 3.4. RELAT紑IO COMPLETO - Filtrado por par滵etros
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense/report?month=1&year=2025
Accept: application/json

###

### 3.5. RELAT紑IO por categoria
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense/report?category=Alimenta誽o
Accept: application/json

###

### 3.6. RELAT紑IO geral (sem filtros)
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense/report
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Atualizar despesa (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
PUT {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": 1,
  "year": 2025,
  "description": "Compra no supermercado - Atualizado",
  "amount": 300.00,
  "category": "Alimenta誽o",
  "status": "Pago",
  "paymentMethod": "Dinheiro"
}

###

### 5. Deletar despesa (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
DELETE {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/expense/1

###

### ========================================
### SUMMARY - Resumo Financeiro
### ========================================

### 6. Buscar resumo financeiro
GET {{WebApplicationAPI_HostAddress}}/api/summary?month=1&year=2025&monthlyIncome=5000
Accept: application/json

